oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Tennessee Centennial Parade on Union Street
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: View looking down Union Street of the buildings and streets decorated for the Tennessee Centennial Parade. American flags are hanging from several buildings. A sign for a Dry Goods store is visible in the background. A few people are walking down the sidewalks, and the street is empty. A sign for The Palace is above a storefront.
